<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
  <h4 class="text-uppercase">Add A New Item</h4>
  <div class="panel ">
    <div class="panel-body">

      <p class="text-bold">If Classfinder++ succesfully sells your book,  a small fee will be incurred, this fee is based on the selling price of the book.
        Click prices below to see the plan.  <br> <button  class = "btn btn-sm my-btn-green" id="bookPrices" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#viewPrices">Prices</button>  </p>
      <%= form_for @book, html: {multipart: true} do |f| %>

          <p>
            <%=render 'shared/error_msgs', object: f.object %>
          </p>
          <p class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :title %><br />
            <%= f.text_field :title, class: 'form-control' %>
          </p>

          <p class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :author %>
            <%= f.text_field :author, class: 'form-control' %>
          </p>

          <!--<p class="form-group">-->
            <!--<label for="item_category_id">Where Is the Exchange Possible</label> <br />-->
            <!--<%# f.check_box @book.institution.all, {:class => "myclass", :style => "mystyle"}, "checked-value", "unchecked-value" %>-->
          <!--</p>-->

          <p class="form-group">
            <label for="item_category_id">Book Belongs In Faculty</label> <br />
            <%= f.select :category_id , Category.where("book_type  = 'Book'").collect {|c| [c.name, c.id]}, { class: 'form-control' } %>
          </p>

          <p class="form-group">
            <label for="item_category_id">Which institution can we get this Book</label> <br />
            <%= f.select :institution_id , Institution.all.collect {|c| [c.name, c]}, { class: 'form-control' } %>
          </p>


          <p class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :description %><br />
            <%= f.text_area :description, class: 'form-control' %>
          </p>

          <div class="form-group">
            <%= f.label :price %>
            <span class="text-bold">: (Rands)</span>
            <%= f.number_field :price, min: 0, step: 'any',  class: 'form-control' %>
          </div>
          <p class="form-g">
            <%= f.label :avatars, "Book Preview Images" %><br />
            <small>To upload many images using PC hold ctrl while selecting images, on your phone long press one image and then you can select many images</small>
            <%= file_field_tag "images[]", type: :file, multiple: true %>
          </p>
          <hr>
          <%= f.submit "Add New Item", class: 'btn btn-flat my-btn' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="viewPrices" class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" style="display: none;">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">Ã—</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title text-bold text-danger">Times and prices</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>A person can purchase your book in organised times and you can also meet a classfinder representative so that we can also get our commision </p>
        <p>Prices if book is:</p>
        <li>R100-300 we take R10</li>
        <li>R301-600 we take R20</li>
        <li>R601-900 we take R30</li>
        <li>R901-1200 we take R40</li>
        <hr>
        <p> The times of meetup are and place is infront of the library</p>
        <li>7:00-8:00</li>
        <li>13:00-14:00</li>
        <li>16:00-17:00</li>
        <hr>
        <p class="text-bold">You need to also check from time to time under my booking tab to see who wants to buy your book</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

